@url=http://localhost:3000

### Login
# @name login
POST {{url}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "esteban",
    "password": "hola123456"
}

###
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Listar todos los viajes
GET {{url}}/viajes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener viaje por id
GET {{url}}/viajes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear nuevo viaje
POST {{url}}/viajes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "vehiculo_id": 2,
    "conductor_id": 3,
    "fecha_salida": "2025-11-12 08:00:00",
    "fecha_llegada": "2025-11-12 16:30:00",
    "origen": "Cordona",
    "destino": "La Rioja",
    "kilometros": 420,
    "observaciones": "Viaje sin novedades"
}

### Actualizar viaje
PUT {{url}}/viajes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "fecha_llegada": "2025-11-12 17:00:00",
    "observaciones": "Demora por lluvia"
}

### Eliminar viaje
DELETE {{url}}/viajes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Consultar historial de viajes por vehiculo
GET {{url}}/viajes/vehiculo/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Consultar historial de viajes por conductor
GET {{url}}/viajes/conductor/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Calcular total de kilometros recorridos por vehiculo
GET {{url}}/viajes/kilometros/vehiculo/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Calcular total de kilometros recorridos por conductor
GET {{url}}/viajes/kilometros/conductor/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}